  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study try to show the weekly cisplatin based CCRT is not inferior to 3-weekly cisplabe
      based CCRT in terms of 3-yr progression free survival rate in advanced nasopharyngeal
      carcinoma
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
